sellerCard.description:
Hello, I'm Umar Sarwar, the Founder of Techy Wizardz, a prominent digital agency specializing in Website Design,WordPress,WIX,Web Flow, PHP, and WordPress Customization. With a commitment to clear communication, I excel in providing exceptional results by truly comprehending your distinct requirements and giving utmost attention to detail.

You can anticipate a cost-effective, premium service with step-by-step guidance at every stage of your project. Timely delivery and efficient project completion are my responsibilities. Let's collaborate to craft something extraordinary together!

description.content:
Hi, My name is Umar and I specialised in developing modern, responsive WordPress website designs for individuals and businesses. With over 7 years of experience, I have successfully completed over 1000 projects for various industries, including Real Estate, Cleaning, Health, Blogging, Kadence, Astra, Construction, eCommerce, affiliate marketing, Membership sites, Wix, and more.


Here's what you can expect from my services:

- WordPress installation

- Elementor Pro licensed for advanced design capabilities

- Content upload

- Mobile and tablet responsiveness

- Enhanced website security measures

- Contact form integration

- Easy-to-manage WordPress dashboard

- Communication throughout the order process very important to achieve final output


Why choose me?

1. Unlimited revisions to ensure your satisfaction

2. Extensive experience in web development spanning 7 years

3. Detailed user manual or video tutorial to empower you in managing your website (if needed)



Let's discuss your requirements further and get started on developing a modern, responsive WordPress website design for your blog or business.


Looking forward to working with you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide hosting and domain
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No I will not provide any hosting and domain if you want then contact me I will tell you which hosting is best for you according to your website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Support period once the order will be completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I respect everyone that's why I will give you free assistance of what I do for 14 DAYS once the order will be completed. 
Moreover, You can ask me for text and image changes once the order will be completed

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide logo or content ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I can provide basic logo and put dummy text or copy from reference website. If you want advance logo then you need to hire some professional for that same as it for content

questionsAndAnswers.question: What about Elementor Pro
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will provide free license for the first year for Elementor pro. If you want to renew second year I can renew at 20$ usd for you

questionsAndAnswers.question: What about Multi-Language Website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will create multi language as well but it will cost more for that you can contact me
